{"tid":1611333,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[退一步諗]盧偉聰請你反省下係邊個導致尋日衝突","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:18:20.000Z","uid":24178,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8c1de0a2ac5905baac2e5367873ce9d3f7c8c9","tid":1611333,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"先唔講多區未開始集會就亂拉人  令到多區衝突<br />\n退一步諗<br />\n點解民陣一開始依足規舉同你攞不反你竟然走去反對<br />\n民陣遊行出名和理非連勇武兄弟做多少少都會俾自己人話<br />\n你批遊行既<br />\n尋日就會好多人出來行 <br />\n行完就散<br />\n你唔洗出來清場<br />\n你唔清自然就唔會有衝突<br />\n<br />\n反問一句<br />\n盧sir 係唔係知道批唔批群眾都會出來<br />\n所以唔批就可以放班手足出來打人殺人?"},{"pid":"f0fa49aec8e62f06535020c9eac024967b1b82b3","tid":1611333,"uid":83217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f3bc0536d6ff9e779c83f0a3595967c992eda6","tid":1611333,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"處心積慮殺人"},{"pid":"c16e0d2c2d3b24fb121d9d78645ddeba89ca9a54","tid":1611333,"uid":7125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n你覺得而家仲係香港啲官話事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇啲手法都知係上面直接落命令啦"},{"pid":"05207acb430ad1b1a34a72f41ddd0b00592e4a8d","tid":1611333,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d23eb23264ead48789cd518300bebae3ac8ab2e7","tid":1611333,"uid":44841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"的確，原本只係想和理非，搶下國際媒體版位，行完就收工。<br />\n唔批根本係錯誤決定。"},{"pid":"4af7845d04e74ba649f0c2f2252d24a5ed1a897a","tid":1611333,"uid":24178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c16e0d2c2d3b24fb121d9d78645ddeba89ca9a54","tid":1611333,"uid":7125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyT